  <num>19-1704.06</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Power to contract: power of appointment not presently exercisable.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>A powerholder of a power of appointment that is not presently exercisable may contract to exercise or not to exercise the power only if the powerholder:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Is also the donor of the power; and</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Has reserved the power in a revocable trust.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
